('CODING','Design a stack that supports push, pop, top, and retrieving minimum element in O(1).','','Use auxiliary min-stack. Push to both when new min. Pop from both when top equals min.','minStack stores current minimum at each level. Push: if val<=minStack.top(), push to minStack.','Easy','Stacks','Amazon','Any',1),
