('CODING','Maximum sum subarray of size k.','','Sliding window: compute sum of first k, then slide by adding new and removing old. O(n).','Initial sum of first k. For i in k..n: sum += arr[i] - arr[i-k]. Track max.','Easy','Sliding Window','Any',NULL,1),
